        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Special Needs Tax Credit Act </b></p> <p>This bill allows an income-based tax credit, up to $5,000 in a taxable year, for legal expenses paid to establish a legal guardianship of a disabled family member. </p>]]>
